data.description: $5,000.00 FLEX CASH. Your pick for rate buy-down, closings costs or price decrease!!! Welcome to this stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home built in 2020 with over 1600 Sq Ft, offering the perfect blend of comfort and convenient living. Located in the heart of Central, this immaculate residence provides a two-car garage, an adaptable bonus room/office upstairs, and an array of fantastic features that are sure to impress. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting floor plan that boasts effortless main-level living. The living area is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. Need a dedicated space for work, creativity, or relaxation? The upstairs bonus room offers endless possibilities, whether you're working from home, creating a playroom, or setting up a cozy reading nook. Step outside onto the large deck and discover the perfect setting for outdoor entertainment and relaxation. The spacious, fenced-in yard provides security and privacy, making it ideal for children and pets to play freely. A convenient dog kennel is ready for your furry family members. This home is perfectly positioned within walking distance to  Central Academy of the Arts, making school drop-offs and pick-ups a breeze. Additionally, you'll appreciate the convenience of being just a short stroll away from downtown Central, where you can explore local shops, dine at charming restaurants, and enjoy community events. This exceptional property won't last long. If you're seeking a modern, move-in-ready home with all the right amenities and an unbeatable location, schedule your viewing today and discover why this could be your dream home! Call for more information or to arrange a private tour. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this house your forever home!
